reviewText: I like this series very much.

The discs are good, there was only one episode that no matter what I will do, it will not finish, so I am having to skip that episode everytime, luckily it was an episode that don't really mind not viewing, but if I was to give this as a gift to someone, I would be really disappointed.

i think that this is a great show, i got it for my friend and they love it
thank you !!!!
